The 12.9 MAX+ isn’t just an awesome keyboard. It represents a new generation of keyboards that form the foundation of our future. 
While our DNA is still the same, every element of the keyboard has been re-designed to create the most precise and perfect keyboard that we’ve ever produced. 
Check out this video from our CEO's to learn more.
